  <brief_title>Clinical Use of Magnetic Resonance Perfusion Imaging to Qualitatively Assess Adequate Distal Perfusion After Endovascular Revascularization in Critical Limb Ischemia</brief_title>
  <acronym>MR CLI</acronym>
