  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the clinical effectiveness of Magnetic Resonance(MR) perfusion imaging
      to qualitatively assess adequate distal perfusion after endovascular revascularization in
      Critical Limb Ischemia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
